# Media Player Integration

The media player system handles video playback, subtitle management, and progress tracking.

## Core Components
- [electron/media-player.ts](mdc:electron/media-player.ts) - Handles media playback functionality
- [src/app/player/page.tsx](mdc:src/app/player/page.tsx) - Player page in the Next.js app

## Features
- Video playback for various formats
- Subtitle detection and display
- Playback progress tracking
- Video quality selection

Note: Some media player features are still under development according to the project roadmap.
